  "title": "微软 CEO 萨提亚·纳德拉 YC 最新访谈：AI 的未来是平台、工具与社会价值 |附全文+视频",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&mid=2247488646&idx=1&sn=fe2e0a01783a768b6078ebcf7ed2214c",
  "date": "2025-06-26 06:15:00",
