  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f035d5c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FV08icaMk7MVb9ibMZRHW7gTiaepzXgia5coObibDwvicVWIW2rgzqwDu70bFp8ob6Efwq2RzVuJVtzpCwp62S4u1RadQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"Web3天空之城\" data-alias=\"Web3SkyCity\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/V08icaMk7MVbppLs8UnGYAUOJELEkxfo0QxOGhP1zvKpjV4X5c6nHQibuV79E4RgCqQeP4VDEAeiaPeQ6wI5QWRHQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"美好的，有趣的，值得铭记的\" data-id=\"MzIxODUzNTg2MA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;\">\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px 8px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Web3天空之城·城主：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在YC（Y Combinator）近日为新一代AI创业者举办的峰会上，微软董事长兼CEO萨提亚·纳德拉也惊喜现身。作为执掌全球最大科技巨轮之一的船长，纳德拉的每一次公开分享都被视为某种行业风向标。在这场对话里，纳德拉以他一贯的宏大而冷静的视角，为我们描绘了一幅关于AI的战略全景图。</span><span leaf=\"\">值得注意的是， 近期微软和OpenAI的合作现在处于某种微妙的博弈之中。相比之下，城主更看好Google自有AI大模型的模式。当然，这些可能都不过是AGI大同路上的一点小插曲罢了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在纳德拉看来，AI并非孤立的技术奇点，而是继客户端-服务器、互联网、移动与云计算之后的第四次重大平台革命。这场革命的终极目的，不是创造拟人化的智能，而是要作为一种普惠工具，为全球经济创造实实在在的“盈余”，并以此换取其存在的“社会许可”。从重塑软件工程的本质，到定义领导力的核心，纳德拉的思考为身处AI浪潮中的每一位建设者，提供了来自顶层设计的清醒洞察。</span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">核心观点摘要</span></strong></h3>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于平台革命的宏大叙事：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“在我35年的人生中，我经历了客户端-服务器、网络互联网、移动云。这是第四次……现在是系统软件的黄金时代。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于AI的社会契约：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你要使用能源，你最好获得使用能源的社会许可。这意味着你必须确保人工智能的输出在社会上是有用的……如果我们真的没有创造社会盈余、经济盈余，那么我们就不能消耗能源。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于AI的本质定位：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我一点也不喜欢将人工智能拟人化。我更多地认为它是一种工具。它不是试图复制我们的思维方式……人类能动性仍然很重要。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于变革的真正瓶颈：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“这种变革管理才是真正的最后限制因素……你现在正在保险公司、金融服务公司、医疗保健公司、软件公司中采用生产方式，并说，我们将改变我们工作方式中的一切。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于软件工程的演变：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们所有人都会创造软件，但仍然会有一种叫做软件工程师的工作。它将会不同……你实际上是把一个软件工程师说成你现在是一个软件架构师。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0.2px 0.2px 0.2px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) rgb(15, 76, 129);margin: 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: italic;padding: 1em 1em 1em 2em;border-radius: 6px;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);background: rgb(247, 247, 247);\">\n    <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 1em;display: block;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">关于领导力的三大支柱：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“领导力的关键在于这神奇的三件事：带来清晰性、创造能量以及通过解决过度约束的问题来驱动成功。”</span></strong></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI作为第四次平台革命</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在纳德拉的战略地图中，AI并非凭空出现的技术浪潮，而是清晰地坐落在计算历史的第四个坐标上。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“在我35年的人生中，我经历了客户端-服务器、网络互联网、移动云。这是第四次，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他开宗明义地指出。他认为，AI之所以能以如此惊人的速度和广度扩散，关键在于它建立在云计算等前代平台的坚实基础之上。这种平台的复合效应，为系统软件带来了前所未有的“黄金时代”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他进一步将AI模型比作一个新时代的SQL数据库引擎。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“在模型层中，我们第一次拥有了类似SQL引擎的东西，然后我们可以用它来构建非常复杂的产品。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在这个范式下，模型本身并非最终应用，而是构建复杂应用的核心组件。初创公司和大型企业的机会，在于如何利用模型这个强大的“新SQL”，结合数据、工具调用和反馈循环，构建出真正有价值的上层应用。他强调，产品内部的数据路径如何反哺模型的后训练，将是未来所有产品创新的核心战场。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI的社会契约：用经济盈余换取能源消耗</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">面对AI模型对算力和能源的无尽需求，纳德拉提出了一个深刻的、关乎其可持续发展的核心命题：AI必须为其巨大的能源消耗证明其存在的合理性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你要使用能源，你最好获得使用能源的社会许可，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他严肃地指出。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“这意味着你必须确保人工智能的输出在社会上是有用的。换句话说，如果我们真的没有创造社会盈余、经济盈余（以国家和社区衡量），那么我们就不能消耗能源。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在他看来，科技行业面临的真正挑战，不是单纯地追求模型基准测试的提升，而是要确保AI的价值能在医疗、教育、公共服务等领域的实际数据中得到体现。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他以医疗行业为例，指出美国高达18%的GDP被用于医疗保健，而其中大量成本消耗在繁琐的工作流程中。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“如果你真的拿像出院这样简单的事情来说，你用LLM和一个提示词就能搞定EMR系统的后端，光是这个就能节省大量的时间、金钱和精力，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他解释道，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“将医生从文书工作中解放出来，把时间分配给病人，这唾手可得。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这种将技术进步直接转化为社会福祉和经济效率的能力，才是AI发展的根本驱动力。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">最后的瓶颈：为何变革管理比技术更难？</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及当前AI部署的最大瓶颈时，纳德拉的答案出人意料地不是技术，而是人与组织的变革。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“这种变革管理才是真正的最后限制因素，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他断言。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他用一个生动的例子解释道，就像个人电脑和Excel的出现，彻底改变了企业做销售预测的工作流程一样，AI的普及也将从根本上重塑工作本身。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“当有人说，我现在要做我的工作了，但我会指挥99个代表我工作的智能代理，那么工作流程就不会保持不变。”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;企业需要重新定义岗位职能，甚至重构整个团队。他提到，LinkedIn已经开始将设计、前端、产品等多个职能融合，催生出“全栈构建者”这样的新角色。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">这种变革的难度在于它的社会性。它要求企业、团队和个人都必须适应新的工作方式。因此，成功的AI产品不仅需要技术上的领先，更需要具备强大的部署和客户成功能力，帮助用户理解并应用新技术，这正是Palantir等公司模式的精髓所在。他认为，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“知识工作中的大量苦工”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是AI最被低估的机会之一，将人们从重复、乏味的“复制粘贴式”工作中解放出来，去从事更具创造性和综合性的思考，将是AI带来的最大价值。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">软件工程的演变：从工程师到架构师</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">对于“AI是否会取代程序员”这一热门话题，纳德拉给出了一个更具建设性的视角：AI不会消灭软件工程师，但会将其提升到新的抽象层次。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他认为，未来的软件开发将更像是人与AI代理的协作。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">我们所有人都会创造软件，但仍然会有一种叫做软件工程师的工作。它将会不同……你实际上是把一个软件工程师说成你现在是一个软件架构师。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在这个新模式下，工程师的核心职责将从编写每一行代码，转变为定义系统架构、审查AI生成的代码、管理代理工作流以及对最终结果负责。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我必须拥有我的代码仓库的元模型以及到底发生了什么，”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;他强调。人类的元认知、判断力以及最终的法律责任，决定了人仍然是整个循环中不可或缺的一环。因此，面向未来的开发工具，如VS Code和GitHub，其核心价值将在于提供强大的画布和工具，让人类能够高效地监督和管理AI代理的工作。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">领导力在AI时代：清晰、能量与解决约束</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在职业生涯的最后，纳德拉分享了他对领导力的深刻洞见，这在AI时代显得尤为重要。他认为，卓越的领导者或团队成员，无论处于何种职位，都应具备三种核心品质：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);list-style: none;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">带来清晰（Bring Clarity）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在模糊、不确定的环境中，能够洞察本质，为团队指明方向。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">创造能量（Create Energy）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;不仅自身充满活力，更能凝聚团队内外的力量，协同作战。</span></p></li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.5em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">3.&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">解决过度约束（Solve Over-Constraints）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;面对看似无解的复杂问题，能够找到关键突破口，解除限制，推动项目成功。</span></p></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">他强调，这些品质并非高层专属，而应是每个有志者在职业生涯每一步都应追求和实践的。</span></p>\n   <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px;border-style: solid;border-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 10%, transparent) rgb(15, 76, 129);font-size: 20.4px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 2.4em;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;padding-left: 12px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);border-radius: 6px;background: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(15, 76, 129) 8%, transparent);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：回归初心，打造赋能于人的新一代工具 | 全文传送</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及如果回到22岁，他会做什么时，纳德拉的回答回归了微软的初心——打造伟大的工具。他将Excel和VS Code这样的产品视为赋能于人的典范，它们给予用户掌控感和强大的分析创造能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 1.5em 8px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">在他看来，Copilot正是这一理念在AI时代的延伸。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(15, 76, 129);\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们能把什么样的工具放在人们手中，让他们拥有那种掌控感？”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这不仅是他个人职业追求的写照，也是他对在场所有AI创业者的终极期许。在这个充满无限可能的时代，技术的最终价值，不在于其自身有多么智能，而在于它能在多大程度上，成为增强人类智慧、创造力和尊严的强大工具。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);margin: 0px;color: rgb(10, 10, 10);font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxODUzNTg2MA==&amp;mid=2247488641&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=dcc355ddc03720b4b9742327ad3d5191&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"【全文版】微软CEO萨提亚·纳德拉：AI的未来是平台、工具与社会价值 |万字+视频\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">【全文版】微软CEO萨提亚·纳德拉：AI的未来是平台、工具与社会价值 |万字+视频</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "微软 CEO 纳德拉在 YC 峰会上阐述 AI 作为第四次平台革命，强调其工具本质及创造社会价值的重要性",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "微软 CEO 纳德拉在 YC 峰会上阐述 AI 作为第四次平台革命，强调其工具本质及创造社会价值的重要性",
  "summary": "微软 CEO 萨提亚·纳德拉在 YC AI 创业者峰会上分享了他对 AI 发展的战略思考。他将 AI 定位为继客户端-服务器、互联网、移动与云计算之后的第四次平台革命，强调 AI 应作为一种普惠工具，为全球经济创造'盈余'以换取其存在的'社会许可'。纳德拉以医疗行业为例，指出 AI 可以简化出院流程等医疗文书工作，将医生时间重新分配给病人。他指出 AI 发展的最大瓶颈不是技术而是组织变革管理，并预测软件工程将向更高抽象层次演变，工程师角色将转变为架构师。他还详细阐述了领导力在 AI 时代的三大支柱：带来清晰性、创造能量和解决过度约束的问题。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 是第四次平台革命，建立在云计算等前代平台基础上",
      "explanation": "纳德拉将 AI 定位为继客户端-服务器、互联网、移动与云计算之后的第四次重大平台变革，强调其系统软件的黄金时代"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 必须创造经济盈余来换取其能源消耗的社会许可",
      "explanation": "纳德拉提出 AI 发展需要证明其社会价值，通过创造医疗、教育等领域的实际效益来获得社会认可，如简化医疗文书工作"
    },
    {
      "point": "组织变革管理是 AI 部署的最大瓶颈而非技术",
      "explanation": "纳德拉认为企业需要重新定义岗位职能和工作流程，催生出'全栈构建者'等新角色，这种社会性变革比技术挑战更难应对"
    },
    {
      "point": "软件工程师将演变为软件架构师的角色",
      "explanation": "未来的软件开发将是人与 AI 代理协作，工程师的核心职责将转向系统架构和 AI 工作流管理"
    },
    {
      "point": "领导力需要带来清晰性",
      "explanation": "在模糊、不确定的 AI 环境中，能够洞察本质，为团队指明方向"
    },
    {
      "point": "领导力需要创造能量",
      "explanation": "不仅自身充满活力，更能凝聚团队内外的力量，协同作战"
    },
    {
      "point": "领导力需要解决过度约束",
      "explanation": "面对看似无解的复杂问题，能够找到关键突破口，解除限制，推动项目成功"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在我 35 年的人生中，我经历了客户端-服务器、网络互联网、移动云。这是第四次......现在是系统软件的黄金时代。",
    "如果你要使用能源，你最好获得使用能源的社会许可。这意味着你必须确保人工智能的输出在社会上是有用的......如果我们真的没有创造社会盈余、经济盈余，那么我们就不能消耗能源。",
    "我一点也不喜欢将人工智能拟人化。我更多地认为它是一种工具。它不是试图复制我们的思维方式......人类能动性仍然很重要。",
    "这种变革管理才是真正的最后限制因素......你现在正在保险公司、金融服务公司、医疗保健公司、软件公司中采用生产方式，并说，我们将改变我们工作方式中的一切。",
    "我们所有人都会创造软件，但仍然会有一种叫做软件工程师的工作。它将会不同......你实际上是把一个软件工程师说成你现在是一个软件架构师。",
    "领导力的关键在于这神奇的三件事：带来清晰性、创造能量以及通过解决过度约束的问题来驱动成功。",
